"01">18. 7. 1910</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">Wien</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb11230">Ehrenstein, Albert</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1910-07-12_02">Ehrenstein an Schnitzler, 12. 7. 1910</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1910-10-09_01">Schnitzler an Ehrenstein, 9. 10. 1910</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
